{"tid":505440,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)王牌大律師-古美門","createTime":"2017-12-21T06:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T13:33:31.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0111833d2d260e182ee09c41d0cba914ba4bf9f3","tid":505440,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:22:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2e5ba878\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b864e5e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d55ffe7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ePyZe4uenxs/UK4xn0qg2jI/AAAAAAAABpI/5Kgi7vODpxU/s1600/legal+high+堺雅人.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ePyZe4uenxs%2FUK4xn0qg2jI%2FAAAAAAAABpI%2F5Kgi7vODpxU%2Fs1600%2Flegal%2Bhigh%2B%E5%A0%BA%E9%9B%85%E4%BA%BA.jpg&h=6ee69aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黛真知子（新垣結衣 飾）是一個充滿著正義感、憑著大無畏的精神，一股腦兒向前衝的熱血新進律師。因為一次訴訟而認識法律界神話&mdash;古美門研介（堺雅人 飾），一位毒舌、傲慢、自大，為了勝訴不擇手段，穿梭在法律灰色地帶但擁有著不敗紀錄的知名律師，此後並開始到古美門律師事務所工作。性格與想法完全地南轅北轍的兩人，在一次又一次的訴訟中不斷發生衝突，但同時又在法庭上攜手戰鬥。一對冤家拍擋緊守各自的信念，衝擊著日本司法界，要在公平與正義之間，還司法制度一個真面目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cb8ae574\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7db39fc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331ecc03c13337a93b918edf7784a56ef37f8b4d","tid":505440,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e789c24ab23b87677f60b78ab834174ced0144","tid":505440,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd1e3b5d38ab87e8949d556193f2a405bc20689","tid":505440,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6a53e89585901961a7378b07d3e5f1590fc51b